{"tid":538876,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"補習師帶學生叫雞當獎勵　全部學生成績突飛猛進","createTime":"2018-01-24T04:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T09:12:17.000Z","uid":29552,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"284d3bba4872b35c9d68c0adbbc6467f0d821d2f","tid":538876,"uid":29552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"南韓一位老師，為了激勵學生好好努力用功，答應他們只要成績變好的話，就帶他們去風俗店買春，事件曝光後，老師被家長告上法院遭判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6d26j8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymotion.com%2Fvideo%2Fx6d26j8&d=n3zzqHPhvY05QAfJB2tZ9lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=f15dd5d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6d26j8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/123244_7bc25ef96a8613204dd373fdc4adae94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F123244_7bc25ef96a8613204dd373fdc4adae94.jpg&h=1883303c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/123244_409e84be4982dc5b06909e51db2b6b42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F123244_409e84be4982dc5b06909e51db2b6b42.jpg&h=d46112d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/123243_91a70a52b6b7a3c93d75d0f2ec3d37a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F123243_91a70a52b6b7a3c93d75d0f2ec3d37a6.jpg&h=c24f906a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓《MBN》1月13日播出的「기막힌 이야기-실제상황」節目中，揭穿了為何成績普通的學生，交給一名補習班名師教導後，成績都可以突飛猛進變成資優生，原來是該位名師跟學生們做了約定，如果成績變好的話，就會帶他們去風俗店買春。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/123244_d59744994e7cae5249f54ced44c609ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F123244_d59744994e7cae5249f54ced44c609ba.jpg&h=b4574a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個獎勵讓學生們在補習班上課時，比在學校還要努力聽課，且課餘時間都會抽空念書，紀律跟毅力也變好了，這樣的狀況讓學生家長相當滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/123243_3ba5977fc7dc7762789468ddc457fbfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F123243_3ba5977fc7dc7762789468ddc457fbfa.jpg&h=c77546f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件會爆發，是因為網路上傳一段在風俗店內偷拍的影片，家長看到這段影片後，發現自己的小孩竟然有入鏡，在追問下才讓家長知道原來名師跟小孩有約定這種特殊獎勵，憤而告上法院。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">這位名師因為違反未成年人保護法，遭法院判10個月監禁，罰款200萬韓元。</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n好人無好報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2da8124b2370d43df66b90d8ecbf20094c270b","tid":538876,"uid":58375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"邊個咁大整蠱？"},{"pid":"4572f5cca072f99af2d0a43987b96ce7e287a336","tid":538876,"uid":60057,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"你俾得D細路返補習社人地交到功課幫你個仔仲要句返人轉頭....咁唔鍾意咪唔好補囉"},{"pid":"d86a9eedd9664eb0af5426ef2a622502d256037a","tid":538876,"uid":14737,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"點解個家長會睇d雞竇偷拍片?"},{"pid":"aad318d17df73249a47dc0ac7c19b457820a1a27","tid":538876,"uid":24759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"一定喺果啲成績差嘅報串啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0db34a3cbdab7445e669675af250903a9506dcd","tid":538876,"uid":4526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"大家都誤會咗牙keith<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f96931c32390b651bb136470de8cfaae2a2a3dc","tid":538876,"uid":29552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a